<h1>Overview</h1>
<p>Three dynamic form implementations:</p>
<ol>
  <li><strong>Schema + Dictionary</strong>: renders fields from a runtime schema to a <code>Dictionary&lt;string, object?&gt;</code>.</li>
  <li><strong>Reflection on POCO</strong>: generates fields from properties and DataAnnotations of a strongly-typed model.</li>
  <li><strong>JSON Schema</strong>: reads schema from <code>wwwroot/schema/customer.json</code> and renders it dynamically.</li>
</ol>
